And particularly,
this little chart--

00:39:57.510 --> 00:40:02.120
I borrow from an interesting
long paper on it,

00:40:02.120 --> 00:40:04.940
is think about the different
parts of the value chain.

00:40:04.940 --> 00:40:07.100
Whether you're sourcing
capital, you're

