00:40:34.470 --> 00:40:37.970
So each of these provides
a little opportunity

00:40:37.970 --> 00:40:41.540
to disrupt the current
business model.

00:40:41.540 --> 00:40:44.350
And so we talked about
payments last class, credit.

00:40:44.350 --> 00:40:46.660
You really have to
get, in a sense,

00:40:46.660 --> 00:40:49.930
granular into which
part of the value chain.

00:40:49.930 --> 00:40:52.510
And then, how do I
bring a technology to it

00:40:52.510 --> 00:40:54.430
that maybe the big
incumbents aren't yet

00:40:54.430 --> 00:40:58.300
doing in a sufficiently
sophisticated way?

00:40:58.300 --> 00:41:00.130
Or you might just
bring it to one sector

